{"id":310875,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/08/韩寒-一时爽罢-不能自拔/","date":"2013-08-27T07:48:00Z","modified":"2013-08-27T07:48:00Z","title":"韩寒 | 一时爽罢 不能自拔","content":"<p>@韩寒：前天成都赛车拿了第二，组委会一反传统，颁发了一个硕大的v字型多孔奖杯。我手贱，对着一个孔插了跟手指玩，结果在领奖台上半天拔不出来。当时正电视直播，我只好挂着奖杯和颁奖嘉宾握手。最后差点用肥皂。今天起床我突然明白了，这一切的寓意原来是：大V，别插手，小心不能脱身，最后让你捡肥皂。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-310876\" alt=\"54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147.jpg\" width=\"500\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147.jpg 1503w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147-256x300.jpg 256w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/08/54ecd80fjw1e813y72xotj215r1cs147-876x1024.jpg 876w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1503px) 100vw, 1503px\" /></a></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,13789],"tags":[8620,23674,10447]}